Yeah.

21:48.551 --> 21:53.056
About his grandfather's Catholic library, where he talks about it being a vegetable.

21:53.117 --> 21:56.681
Did you show... You tell him about De Gaulle, because that's the manuscript of De Gaulle.

21:56.701 --> 21:58.343
Did you show Nick those...

21:58.880 --> 22:00.422
wash manuscripts?

