32:07.507 --> 32:07.867
Oh, he did.

32:07.887 --> 32:08.709
Significantly.

32:08.969 --> 32:10.411
From what he had done in the first.

32:10.431 --> 32:12.213
So this stuff was going to Firestone?

32:12.233 --> 32:13.936
So, I'll get back to that story.

32:14.296 --> 32:15.337
Don't forget it.

32:15.377 --> 32:16.038
I won't forget it.

32:16.058 --> 32:18.662
Here's a little collection, the Robert Linscott Group.

32:19.403 --> 32:21.345
That's all there was, but that's pretty interesting.

32:21.406 --> 32:25.551
